sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant K as Kernel
    participant R as Retriever
    participant V as Vector DB
    participant L as LLM
    U->>K: Query
    K->>R: Retrieve context
    R->>V: Similarity search
    V-->>R: Top-k chunks
